                        <div class="bg-primary rounded d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                            <i class="fa fa-award text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Award Winning</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">As an award-winning company, we take pride in our dedication to excellence and innovation. Each accolade reflects our commitment to delivering outstanding solutions and services that exceed expectations, solidifying our reputation as a trusted leader in the industry.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4  wow zoomIn" data-wow-delay="0.9s" style="min-height: 350px;">
                <div class="position-relative h-100">
