                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 wow zoomIn" data-wow-delay="0.8s">
                        <div class="bg-primary rounded d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
                            <i class="fa fa-phone-alt text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4>24/7 Support</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">We offer 24/7 support to ensure that help is always available when you need it. Our dedicated team is committed to providing prompt, reliable assistance around the clock, so you can stay focused on what matters most.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
